- Tracks 7-8 originally released as Systral / Acheborn "A Split Seven Inch" 7'' on Trans Solar Records (1998)
- Track 10 originally released on "The 51 Comp" Compilation" LP on Join The Team Player Records (1997)
- Tracks 12-18 originally released as "Tuesday Is Dead" LP/CD on Trans Solar (1999)
- Track 20 originally released on "The Seed Of The Next Season" Compliation LP on Per Koro Records/Alveran Records (1999)
- Tracks 22 & 23 previously unreleased

Acheborn was:
André Liegl, Heikki Eiden, Jens Wucherpfennig, Sascha Salipurovic and Steffen Heller.
